				<td colspan="2"><span>Simple:
<br />

<br />
Cast Amp
<br />
Cast dot 1
<br />
Cast dot 2
<br />
Cast dot 3
<br />
Cast dot 4
<br />
Recast 1-4
<br />
Wash/repeat
<br />

<br />
Don't sweat that your dot drops *just* before you recast... or that you lose 2-3 when you cast amp... amp is WAY worth the 3 seconds and 4 dots make the druids/shammies look your way in awe.  =)
<br />

<br />
I play this set when I'm duoing with a rooter, typically a tranq'd shammy, so I don't have to twist-in mana.</span></td>
