				<td colspan="2"><span>It is possible (but with missed notes and resists highly highly unlikely) to stack 5 dots.  I think the parsing that was done indicated you could do 4 with about 95% reliability but the reliability of landing 5 dropped to below 60%.  So for max consistent dot damage, load your best drum and twist 4 of the POP chants.  The value is more damage, more debuff.  Is it worth 25K?  Probably not to most people, but your mileage may vary.</span></td>
