If you dont have any missed notes, you can get 5 dots, since you dont have to twist assonance back in until it wears off.  Then you will drop to 3 or 4 till you get it to stick again.  Once it sticks again, you twist back in all 4, and you can get all 4 chants, and Assonance, again</span></td>
